Taxonomy

Supervised: fit a function wrt to a criterion
  Regression : fit a function (fit its parameters) wrt the MSE criterion
  Classification : fit a function wrt to a cross
-> collect names of methods

data sources:
- scalar (voltage, vibrations)
- time series (temperature, pressure)
- images (IR thermography)
what methods for each?

data flow:
collect, analyse, predict, react
analyze include: data cleaning, feature selection/engineering, method selection, hyperparameter tuning.

Data properties and quality:
- amount of data: data is often scarce
- noise, errors, missing data
- high-dimensional data
- class imbalance
- heterogeneous data (scalars, booleans, time series, images, text)

Besoin de :
- visualiser données
- automatiser la détection d'anomalies
- automatiser la prédiction de RUL / failures

Accuracy criteria : cf taxonomy.
- Precision, recall, F1, ROC

